<div class="card">
    <div class="card-header bg-dark text-light">Level 3</div>
    <div class="card-body">
        <p>Using the SportsORM, complete all the following queries and show their results on Level3.cshtml.</p>
        <ol>
            <li>...all teams, past and present, that Samuel Evans has played with</li>
            <ul>
                @foreach(var team in ViewBag.SamEvans.AllTeams){
                    <li>@team.TeamOfPlayer.TeamName</li>
                }
            </ul>
            <li>...all players, past and present, with the Manitoba Tiger-Cats</li>
            <ul>
                @foreach(var player in ViewBag.TigerCats.AllPlayers){
                    <li>@player.PlayerOnTeam.FirstName @player.PlayerOnTeam.LastName has played for the @ViewBag.TigerCats.Location @ViewBag.TigerCats.TeamName</li>
                }
                @foreach (var plyr in ViewBag.TigerCats.CurrentPlayers)
                {
                    <li>@plyr.FirstName @plyr.LastName plays for the @ViewBag.TigerCats.Location @ViewBag.TigerCats.TeamName</li>
                }
            </ul>
            <li>...all players who were formerly (but aren't currently) with the Wichita Vikings</li>
            <ul>
                @foreach(var player in ViewBag.FormerVikings.AllPlayers){
                    <li>@player.PlayerOnTeam.FirstName @player.PlayerOnTeam.LastName has played for the @ViewBag.FormerVikings.Location @ViewBag.FormerVikings.TeamName</li>
                }
            </ul>
            <li>...every team that Jacob Gray played for before he joined the Oregon Colts</li>
            <ul>
                @foreach (var team in ViewBag.Gray.AllTeams)
                {
                    <li>@team.TeamOfPlayer.Location @team.TeamOfPlayer.TeamName</li>
                }
            </ul>
            <li>...everyone named "Joshua" who has ever played in the Atlantic Federation of Amateur Baseball Players</li>
            <li>...all teams that have had 12 or more players, past and present.</li>
            <li>...all players, sorted by the number of teams they've played for</li>
        </ol>
    </div>
</div>